Explaining the approach for the closure.

1) Start recording with SAP recorder
2) Go to ME22N and carry out the steps to mark delevery completion
3) Save the recording and open the file where the recording is saved
4) This is a VB code- insert while loop so that we can close multiple PO
5) Save the code
6) Open Excel, add a button 
7) Assign macro to this button and sleect our recorded file.

Done! You now have a file which can access SAP and close PO remotely.
